                <expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex>ilvano</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>omestico</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>acrum</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Aufidia <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Gentina <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Altar oder Basis; auf der Oberseite rechteckige Einlassung. Z. 2: Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Lesung nach I. Weber-Hiden. (B): Stiglitz: Z. 2/3: Avid(ia) Cres/centina; Stiglitz; AE 2008: Z. 4: v(otum) s(olvit) l(ibens) l(aeta) m(erito).</p>
            </div>
